extendedInfo.description: This is the #1 Dubstep ringtone app series on the android market, and is an absolute MUST HAVE for all Dub step DJ fans! This compilation soundboard contains 24 of the filthiest drops and dirtiest beats available for your mobile device. This app will be updated regularly, so download with confidence and don't forget to check out my other apps! "Super Digital Clock Widget" can be easily customized with more than 100 fonts and any color to match your electro theme or live wallpaper, so check it out as well!Features:Hi-res graphics and rich user experience.Lots of dubstep sounds, of course!Tap to toggle sound on and off.Press and hold button to save as a ringtone, notification, or alarm tone.Assign tones to contacts.***************IMPORTANT!!!!TO SAVE A RINGTONE, PRESS AND HOLD THE BUTTON OF THE SOUND THAT YOU WANT TO SAVE AND IT WILL INSTALL TO YOUR SYSTEM RINGTONES.(Settings->Sound->Phone Ringtone)(Settings->Sound->Notification Ringtone)In order to give you a free app and keep developing more free apps in the future, we are integrating a search tool to our application. This will add a few access points to your device (hence the permissions) to direct you to the web search service. Please consider using the search to help us keep creating apps. You may delete the search icon, bookmark and homepage easily. Thank you.This app is ad supported to enable me to continue development and add new features. If you want the ad-free version, you can find it here on the market with my other apps. Big thanks to all of the artists featured for bringing the noise!***************
